    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-500 to-green-600 p-0.5">
          <div class="w-full h-full rounded-[9px] bg-white flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xl">üç™</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-wider">Configuraci√≥n de Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-[10px] text-lime-600 font-medium">Privacidad m√≠nima garantizada</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Utilizamos cookies propias y de terceros para mejorar tu experiencia. Al aceptar, nos ayudas a optimizar la web. Puedes leer m√°s en nuestra <a href="/cookies/" class="text-slate-900 hover:text-lime-600 underline transition-colors">Pol√≠tica de Cookies</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <button id="accept-cookies" class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-lime-500 to-green-600 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all outline-none">
          Aceptar todas
        </button>
        <button id="reject-cookies" class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-slate-200 hover:text-slate-900 active:scale-95 transition-all outline-none">
